.TH RUNMIRRORS.MIRROR 5 "2026-03-27" "ctxos-core 1.0.0" "CTX OS Manual"
.SH NAME
runmirrors.mirror \- mirror definitions for runmirrors
.SH DESCRIPTION
Defines the list of downstream mirrors for runmirrors.
Each line specifies a mirror entry.
.SH FORMAT
Lines starting with # are comments. Each non-empty line has the format:
.PP
.RS
\fITYPE NAME HOSTNAME USER SSHOPTS\fR
.RE
.SH TYPES
.TP
.B staged
Push to a staging area.
.TP
.B mhop
Multi-hop push.
.TP
.B DELAY
Insert a delay between pushes.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR runmirrors (1),
.BR runmirrors.conf (5)
